articles.title: Olivia Colman: Uneasy Lies the Head That Wears the Crowns
articles.description: Olivia Colman has been a quiet star in Britain for a decade. But with two royal roles ahead, she’s reluctantly stepping into the spotlight.
articles.content: I was such a massive fan of the show, and I thought Claire Foy was just breathtaking, she said. I no idea they were going to recast for season 3 and 4, so hadnt thought about the role at all. She did an imitation of her agent calling her and trying to be disc… [+1759 chars]
